graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|container platform| OpenShift[OpenShift/Kubernetes 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine v2| ArgoWorkflows[Argo Workflows 3.x]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine v1 deprecated| Tekton[Tekton Pipelines 1.8+]
    DSPO -->|authentication| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy v4.12.0+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - can be deployed or external)
    DSPO -.->|metadata storage| MariaDB[MariaDB 10.3+ / MySQL 5.7+]
    DSPO -.->|artifact storage| S3Storage[S3-compatible Storage]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|deployed by| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator]
    DSPO -->|UI integration| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% Platform Components
    DSPO -->|uses| CertManager[service-serving-cert-signer]
    DSPO -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus / monitoring.coreos.com]

    %% Integration Points
    ODHDashboard -->|displays runs| DSPO
    ODHDashboard -->|links to UI| DSPO

    %% Deployment Options
    subgraph "Storage Options"
        DeployedMinio[Minio<br/>Deployed by DSPO]
        ExternalS3[External S3<br/>AWS/Compatible]
    end

    subgraph "Database Options"
        DeployedMariaDB[MariaDB<br/>Deployed by DSPO]
        ExternalDB[External MySQL/MariaDB<br/>User-managed]
    end

    DSPO -.->|option 1: deploys| DeployedMinio
    DSPO -.->|option 2: connects| ExternalS3
    DSPO -.->|option 1: deploys| DeployedMariaDB
    DSPO -.->|option 2: connects| ExternalDB

    %% Execution Engines
    subgraph "Execution Engine Options"
        ArgoV2[Argo Workflows<br/>DSP v2 - Current]
        TektonV1[Tekton Pipelines<br/>DSP v1 - Deprecated]
    end

    DSPO -->|v2 pipelines| ArgoV2
    DSPO -.->|v1 pipelines deprecated| TektonV1

    %% External Services
    DSPO -.->|pulls images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io, registry.redhat.io]

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (required)
    style OpenShift fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ArgoWorkflows fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Tekton fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style OAuthProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Optional dependencies
    style MariaDB fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style S3Storage fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH
    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ODHDashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Platform
    style CertManager fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#dae8fc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Storage options
    style DeployedMinio fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ExternalS3 fill:#fff2cc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Database options
    style DeployedMariaDB fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ExternalDB fill:#fff2cc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Execution engines
    style ArgoV2 fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TektonV1 fill:#f8cecc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% External services
    style ContainerRegistry fill:#fff2cc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
